(for p being (Point of ( TopSpaceMetr M1 )) holds (for V being  open (Subset of ( TopSpaceMetr M1 )) holds (for q being (Point of M2) holds ((q = ( f . p ) & p in V) implies (ex r being  positive  real number st ( Ball (q,r) ) c= ( f .: V ))))))
proof
